tile.space_warp_pad.description: 傳送墊允許你傳送到各個太空維度,需要擺成3x3的形狀.
tile.rocket_crusher.description: 火箭粉碎機可將火箭變成重裝防護板.它需要用在火箭工作檯裡.
tile.cheese_milk_cake.description: Cheese Milk Cakes are created from Cheese Milk Curds from Chalos, placeable and edible.
tile.dark_energy_receiver.description: 暗黑能量無線接收器將從銀河系遙遠星系收集未知能量,用來製造暗黑能量機器.非常危險!
tile.dark_energy_core.description: 從未知遙遠星系來的強大方塊.將物品放在方塊頂部,可將物品變成宇宙中難獲得的東西.
tile.nuclear_waste_generator.description: 核廢料發電機能收集附近區域核廢料的輻射來產生巨大能量.
dark_energy_storage_cluster.description: Dark Energy Storage Cluster is used to store large amounts of energy for later use. Stores and outputs more energy than its predecessors.
nuclear_waste_energy_storage_cluster.des: Nuclear Waste Energy Storage Cluster is used to store large amounts of energy for later use. Stores and outputs more energy than its predecessors.
tile.dark_energy_generator.description: 暗黑能量發電機將從遙遠未知的星球或暗黑能量珍珠收集能量,儲存以進一步使用.
tile.black_hole_storage.description: 黑洞物品儲存器是一個用黑洞吸取物品/經驗的大型物品儲存器.物品和經驗將用其設定儲存.
tile.shield_generator.description: 屏障發生器將保護玩家不受危險事物(怪物,拋體)的傷害並且它仍WIP.
tile.sealable_nuclear_waste_rod.descript: 密封方塊需要用在空氣無法進入的地方,比如太空底牆.
item.infected_arrow.description: 可將箭丟入被感染的水獲得.
